reviewText: I purchases this as a Christmas gift, the receiver loved it.

The flick was good, it was good to see the younger gen comming through. i like the fact that the old tricks are still there,

nothen to change about how it was presented, keep up the good work.
"This is my element" is a great skate DVD and it stars some of the best skaters that no longer skate for element any more. Love the dvd and i recommend it to everyone, while you can still get a copy.
This video was bought for my 13 year old son as a Christmas present. He was very happy to receive it and enjoyed watching it.
